dialogueList.name: Coco
dialogueList.text: Hey Player,its Coco, glad to see you back on the track, its been a long time coming.

dialogueList.name: Coco
dialogueList.text: Oh, so you're scared to race properly? Fiiine let's do the beginner track.

dialogueList.name: NARRATOR
dialogueList.text: This is the Beginner racetrack, this is where you'll learn to drive against other beginner drivers, race to the finish.

dialogueList.name: NARRATOR
dialogueList.text: Use WASD to move. Good luck driver.
